Gradient ascent
\series default
\color inherit
: find 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{\max}$
\end_inset

 by iterating until convergence:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{k+1}=x_{k}+\underset{\text{learning rate}}{\underbrace{\gamma}}\cdot\underset{\text{gradient}}{\underbrace{f'(x_{k})}}
\]

